findings.title: Abuse of authority
findings.description: The owner has excessive privileges to change critical contract settings and perform sensitive operations such as minting and burning.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges to modify critical parameters and perform sensitive operations such as minting and burning tokens, changing crowdSale and preICOSale addresses, updating locked amounts, making presale ICO locking, and changing LockingLimit.
